Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] We played together often\Nwhen we were very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But later, as I\Nstarted to grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING] Your brother Bojji\Nis a pitiable child,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,feeble in body and mind.\NHelpless on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NAnd for this reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it is your duty to become strong\Nenough to protect him, Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't fail you, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] After that,\NI first met the Mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NHow do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's talking! This mirror talks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] I could count on it to\Nprovide me with valuable advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, with the praise\NI so desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] You are among\Nthe chosen, Prince Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the few born into\Nthis world destined to reign
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,over its people as their king.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] Soon... without\Nrealizing it myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...I came to see\Nmy brother as a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NBebin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Must we go to such\Nlengths to accommodate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,my weakling of a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Prince\NBojji is a weakling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:02:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NIt's been a while, Prince Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you care\Nto visit town with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOYS giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOY 11B]\NHey, what's over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NWhy did we come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[SORII] A chance to see\Nthe people of the kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,up close, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NPointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[SORII] A chance to explore\Nsome hypotheticals, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\N"Hypotheticals"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to live\N100 years, Prince Daida?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd!\NWho'd want to live that long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That being the case,\Nis the idea of living
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,90 years more appealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that still\Ntoo long for your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorii... What are\Nyou getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[SORII chuckles]\NOnly making idle chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I've spotted someone\Nyou'd call a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One far worse off\Nthan Prince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Worse off in what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of them can hear,\Nbut your brother is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the more fortunate.\NThat man is blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would one\Ncarry on existing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To bear that burden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To survive on pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I would sooner end my own life\Nthan live that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then fate has\Nset greater challenges
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,before him than you\Nare willing to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, this man you'd\Ncall weak is pressing on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,when you say you would not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just doublespeak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could ask him, I doubt\Nhe would think anything of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the burden you describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been able to carry on\Nliving despite his afflictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...he can thank your father,\Nand the prosperous kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he's built.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Daida. Our\Ngoal is to instill in you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the strength to bring hope\Nto everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was... a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you come from?!\NCan you get back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to get\Nout of here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NI didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- I did nothing!\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NI'm scared... Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop. It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please stop"?! Did you listen\Nwhen we said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinous villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How could someone be so cruel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All this misery is on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN 11C]\NApologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- [GIRL] No, I didn't!\N- [MAN 11D] You abomination!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NIt's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NYour hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What... is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS]\NLiars! They're all lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand any of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 11A]\NThat girl you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster killed all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 11A]\NUs and so many more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our deaths were painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The suffering was unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our land was peaceful.\NGreat and plentiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our people, marked\Nby kindness and wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 11A] They invaded our\Ndomain, and what little they
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't tear asunder,\Nthey stole for themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS]\NNo! That isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NMy mask... It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- [laughter]\N- [DAIDA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- [GIRL] Where is my mask?\N- [laughter continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where is it...?\N- [laughter continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where did it go? Please...\N- [laughter continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm scared...\N- [laughter continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!\N- [GIRL] That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What... are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster. You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NYou're wrong! I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little girl. And one day,\NI'm going to be a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 11B]\NShe's quite hideous, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 11A]\NWe made her that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN 11B]\NWith our own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We flayed the skin from her\Nface so all who look at her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,will see the mark of her sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And we cut off her hands\Nto prevent her from resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- [DAIDA whimpers]\N- [GIRL sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN 11E whimpers]\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN 11B]\NStop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[blows thudding]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Daida. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NMiranjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miranjo. Don't let them\Nbring you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She has been stained\Nwith the blood of hundreds
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of victims like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,These are her just desserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a right to retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want her, then fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO]\NThat smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO] Have you ever\Nmet a man named "Bosse"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO]\NYou have the same smell as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,His smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean... you also\Nknow my father somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father? Bosse is your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bosse I know\Nhas no children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,More to the point,\Nhow did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO]\NThank you for coming to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay with me.\NIt'll be safer that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO]\NOh. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NHmm... No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother will be coming\Nto get me out of here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO]\NGet you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] That's right.\NAnd you'll be coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO]\NI will?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to get\Nout of this place together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it. Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NWhat is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though a weight\Nwas lifted from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[SERVANT 11A snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Hah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! King Desha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[SERVANT 11A]\NYes, sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESHA]\NHmm? Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Empty?! But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESHA]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[SERVANT 11A]\NGuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESHA sniffs] A faint\Nlingering smell of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,King Desha... I've failed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't done any such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This has been set into\Nmotion by outside forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,making use of a power\Nwe'd thought lost until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[SERVANT 11A]\NA lost power, sire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Should that power\Nreach the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it would become\Na problem for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Order of the\NUnderworld's commander. Ouken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A man whose fighting\Ntechniques defy explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,known throughout our\Nland as the Sword King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]\NSummon the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[SERVANT 11A gasps]\NYes, sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Onward. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE panting]\NPlease wait, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[wheezing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not built for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll rest once\Nwe reach the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NBe strong, Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NI have Dorshe with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,along with these\Nhardened soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NHokuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is even this beyond you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- [DOMAS grunting]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It works splendidly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NCould he be any worse a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He only knows\Nhow to train himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I want to learn the sword,\NI'll have to learn it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's on your mind?\N- [HOKURO squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NThe day we seal the gate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Underworld\Nis approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,King Bosse told me to expect\Nsome event to signal us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,when the time arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it? Did he say\Nanything more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He said no more\Nthan what I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... This all feels ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It almost seems like King Bosse\Nis covering for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But for who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Miranjo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[metal clanging]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS grunts, groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Miranjo, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[screeches]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO] What are you\Nso afraid of, Apeas?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps your confidence\Nhas been stolen away by those
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,who lacked confidence in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown to like you\Nquite a bit since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours is such a tender heart,\Nand so easily hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But for this, you readily\Nunderstand the pain of others
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and that endears you to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of what you see was\Nnot born, but fabricated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My smile has no warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are a growing being\Nwith boundless potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply envision\Nthe man you wish to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have faith in me, and believe\Nin yourself as I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO]\NThere, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds will take time\Nto heal, as all wounds do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO]\NBut slowly, little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you will become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS]\NI've been expecting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Miranjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESHA] It would appear\Nthe escaped criminals have fled
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Kingdom of Bosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You must capture them\Nimmediately, without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, with old Bosse's\Npassing, his nation was left
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,on the verge of civil war.\NSo, accordingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...when we capture the\Nfugitives, we'll also be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,capturing the Kingdom of Bosse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NThanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done so much\Nfor us, Despa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more grateful to you\Nthan I know how to put in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've enjoyed our time\Ntogether, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] We'll be back\Nto visit, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NYou're welcome any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-au, awaw, ah-deh-dah.\NAwa, dau.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to fret.\NWe will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, when\Nexactly did you come up with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a way to understand Bojji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I never did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI, KAGE]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know a bit\Nof sign language.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... A-Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What about those rules\Nfor carrying a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes. Of course I\Nwould recognize the words
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd had him recite\Nback to me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Understand"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NAh. Even so. Bojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me when\NI say that your gratitude could
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,hardly be more apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I should thank you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Teaching you has been\Nimmensely rewarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Know this. You may feel\Nweaker for what you lack,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but in fact, its absence could\Nbe a source of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] It has led you to chart\Nyour own path through the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a path most people\Ncould never hope to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And though your journey\Nhas been painful at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,through your experience\Nyou've grown strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to see it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji, you should love\Neverything about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Au!\N- Courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Despa!\NWe'll always be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh-wa, au!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[horse neighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 5A]\NWhoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Jeez! Did you really\Nneed to send this many guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 5A]\NPrince Bojji, please hop on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?\NThey're giving us a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually. A group of\Nunderworld criminals escaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're believed to have\Nentered the Kingdom of Bosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Seems like scary stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,King Desha has\Ndeployed these soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to pursue said criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow them\Nto bring you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 5A] Quickly!\NThere's no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NMm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye and godspeed\Nto both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NWhoo! We're really movin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Au, au, au-au. Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back at the castle way\Nsooner than I thought we would!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When we capture the fugitives,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll also be capturing\Nthe Kingdom of Bosse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHey, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 5A]\NHmm?! Ahem. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, just wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of underworld\Ncriminals are we
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,dealing with, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 5A]\NA fair question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Vicious, violent brutes,\Neach and every one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Black the Brunet\Nand Red the Copperhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Professional killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The massive Gigan,\Nbearing a terribly powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,metal-clad body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The bandit Zokku, leader\Nof the hoards of brigands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,roaming the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Almighty Kingbo, long\Nsince fallen from the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly, the Sword King of\Nthe Underworld, Ouken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Each is frightfully\Npowerful in his own right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Au, au! Au, dah, awa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 5A]\NWhat did Prince Bojji say?
